Docs.summary: A Delegate type used to add an event handler for the event. The AfterXmlExport event occurs after Microsoft Excel saves or exports data from the specified workbook to an XML data file.

remarks.para: XML features, except for saving files in the XML Spreadsheet format, are available only in Microsoft Office Professional Edition 2003 and Microsoft Office Excel 2003.
